# ğŸ©º MediChat Assist

**MediChat Assist** is a modern web application that provides medical chat assistance through a clean, responsive UI. Built with **React (or Next.js)**, styled using **Tailwind CSS**, and deployed via **Firebase Hosting**, this app combines real-time interaction with elegant design.

